MGM/UA Communications Co saidit has joined Paramount Pictures and MCA Inc's &lt;MCA> UniversalStudios in their agreement with China Film Corp of Beijing todistribute motion pictures in China.    MGM said it is also joining a venture to license two hoursa week of primetime television programming to China's nationaltelevision network.    Revenues will be derived from advertising time for U.S. andforeign companies, it said. Reuter&#3;